    public class RoundRobinByTime
extends AbstractAllocator
    Allocates a workitem to a participant on a round-robin basis, to the participant who has not performed the task for the longest time. Create Date: 23/08/2007. Last Date: 12/11/2007
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Michael Adams (BPM Group, QUT Australia)
